org.openide.windows

Class IOTab

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openide.windows.IOTab

  • public abstract class IOTab
extends Object
    Settings of tool tip/icon for IO component (tab).

    Client usage: 

      // settings of IO tab icon, tooltip
  InputOutput io = ...;
  Icon icon = ...;
  IOTab.setIcon(io, icon);
  IOTab.setToolTipText(io, "text");
    How to support IOTab in own IOProvider implementation:
    • InputOutput provided by IOProvider has to implement Lookup.Provider
    • Extend IOTab and implement its abstract methods
    • Place instance of IOTab to Lookup provided by InputOutput
    Since:
    1.15
